    (ROPC_Credentials_Used( ClientID, pw ) @ #i) ⇒
    (((¬(∃ #j. K( pw ) @ #j)) ∨ (∃ #r. RevealPassword( pw ) @ #r)) ∨
     (∃ skC #r. RevealClientKey( ClientID, skC ) @ #r))"
/*
guarded formula characterizing all counter-examples:
"∃ ClientID pw #i.
  (ROPC_Credentials_Used( ClientID, pw ) @ #i)
 ∧
  (∃ #j. (K( pw ) @ #j)) ∧
  (∀ #r. (RevealPassword( pw ) @ #r) ⇒ ⊥) ∧
  (∀ skC #r. (RevealClientKey( ClientID, skC ) @ #r) ⇒ ⊥)"
*/
